{"tid":45340,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句，香港地買車係戇鳩，買公路單車才是明智之舉","createTime":"2016-12-19T02:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T17:18:22.000Z","uid":38539,"like":13,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de9e3b2caacc0f9845f3e23a45af5312672d5eb0","tid":45340,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:10:35.000Z","msg":"一架公路單車價錢都只是萬鬆 <br />\n香港好細 四通發達 單車在手 完全任你行 <br />\n唔怕塞車 唔洗供車位 維修費又唔貴<br />\n出街唔驚無位泊 隨街泊又唔怕抄牌<br />\n唔洗考牌 唔驚比人扣分<br />\n超音速唔怕比人捉 不過可能上youtube<br />\n在馬路上所有車手都忌你三分 <br />\n在行人路人上響鈴岳飛也要讓步<br />\n簡直係馬路上o的皇者 行人路上o的剋星<br />\n給我一個原因買車？不了，有公路單車"},{"pid":"af72aecf0f1fe11a958eb29938e95742d75361a8","tid":45340,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:12:15.000Z","msg":"潮文？"},{"pid":"6519431191221ea013c4531ede8e57675d5a9e4c","tid":45340,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>潮文？</blockquote><br />\n認真post <br />\n是本人琴晚睇完長騎美眉<br />\n係床上細味時所領悟出黎o的真理"},{"pid":"4186fa8db8d25f1a95323109640bd967639c5f64","tid":45340,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:21:57.000Z","msg":"踩馬路成日俾的士小巴夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明唔係慢 多數燈位追番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386cae5df4137440fa645f79e5415899eca6d35d","tid":45340,"uid":43611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:23:01.000Z","msg":"琴晚先見到有公路車手比人炒低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc2fd92b75b6abb8f5ef9c3617d8e4611e4266c","tid":45340,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:23:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb1b1dbe9c304ed48df0e8da83025c926289b11","tid":45340,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:25:49.000Z","msg":"<b